{"tid":1656792,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《視點31》【死因有無可疑？】還公眾一個真相","createTime":"2019-10-15T19:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:37:19.000Z","uid":64426,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8a614bae108540ba274209bb61a638eca52eec","tid":1656792,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VKO_DqiwwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3VKO_DqiwwU&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLL9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e85daee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VKO_DqiwwU</a><br />\n<br />\n馬宣立指<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">家人絕對有權要求死因庭召開聆訊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n馬宣立亦透過其他國家的同行打聽後指出<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即使因海嘯遇難的死者都好少會沖走衣服導致裸體</span></span><br />\n<br />\n召開死因聆訊警犬就一定唔撚會做，但如果佢屋企都唔做既，咁佢屋企人有好撚可疑，點解有機會知彥霖係自殺定他殺既時候會連召開既動機都無？<br />\n<br />\n同埋彥霖既隨身物品又去撚左邊，彥霖遇溺既地方附近有無搜過，有無燒野既痕跡等等，警犬係咪有必要交代下呢？"},{"pid":"5c0b9318c7e27852cf8f9f048d5cf109c3107656","tid":1656792,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"b235ccb98bd9192283d375c96c4ca6f44654107e","tid":1656792,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:09:01.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"1f43423b7e8b66089d8ec5cf501442f4a320ff58","tid":1656792,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"c94e31ddc92ebf627bc159e645449f7f12f8c0c4","tid":1656792,"uid":310328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"如果陳彥霖行去自殺無着鞋 佢對鞋係邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d844956e3288a9dc9e7d0c2cbbf0f803306104ce","tid":1656792,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi